This topic contains release notes for Healthwatch v2.2.

The architecture of Healthwatch v2.2 is entirely different from the architecture of Pivotal
Healthwatch v1. Healthwatch v2.2 uses the open-source components Prometheus, Grafana, and Alertmanager
to scrape, store, and view metrics, as well as configure alerts. For more information about
the differences between Pivotal Healthwatch v1 and Healthwatch v2.2 and how to upgrade to Healthwatch
v2.2, see [Upgrading Healthwatch](upgrading-healthwatch.html).

For information about the risks and limitations of Healthwatch v2.2, see [Assumed Risks of
Using Healthwatch v2.2](index.html#assumed-risks) and [Healthwatch v2.2 Limitations](index.html#healthwatch-limitations)
in _Healthwatch_.


